OL,3,CPlastic surgeon found guilty of
OL,4,Cattempting to murder fellow doctor in
OL,5,Cwork feud
OL,7,FA plastic surgeon has been found
OL,8,Fguilty of trying to kill a fellow
OL,9,Fsurgeon by stabbing him, after he
OL,10,Fattempted to set his house on fire.
OL,12,FDr Jonathan (Peter) Brooks, 61, was
OL,13,Fconvicted of two counts of attempted
OL,14,Fmurder, attempted arson with intent to
OL,15,Fendanger life, and possession of a
OL,16,Fknife in a public place, after he
OL,17,Fattacked former colleague Graeme Perks
OL,18,Fin the early hours of January 14, 2021.
