OL,4,Cattempting to murder fellow doctor in
OL,5,Cwork feud
OL,7,FJurors deliberated for more than 12
OL,8,Fhours before finding Brooks guilty of
OL,9,Fall the charges against him.
OL,11,FProsecutors said Brooks, doused the
OL,12,Fground floor of the property in petrol
OL,13,Fbefore stabbing Mr Perks, who he
OL,14,F"hated" because he was giving evidence
OL,15,Fin a work disciplinary hearing against
OL,16,Fthe defendant.
OL,18,FBoth men are former plastic surgeons
OL,19,Fat Nottingham City Hospital.
