OL,7,FMr Perks, who was aged 65 at the time
OL,8,Fof the attack, had only recently
OL,9,Fretired.
OL,11,FLoughborough Court heard Dr Brooks, a
OL,12,Fspecialist in burns and plastics,
OL,13,Fcycled to Mr Perks' house in Halam,
OL,14,FNottinghamshire, in the early hours of
OL,15,FJanuary 14, 2021.
OL,17,FProsecutors said Brooks doused the
OL,18,Fground floor of the property in petrol
OL,19,Fbefore stabbing Mr Perks.
